    <item>
      <title>交易员称比特币 ETF 预示着长期内代币热度将有所下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/bitcoin-etfs-herald-less-febrile-token-longer-term-traders-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周初，比特币一路走低，引发了人们对美国交易所交易基金资金外流的担忧。然而，逢低买入的买家却大量涌入现金，从某种程度上来说，这种模式表明，从长期来看，比特币的波动性会更小。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-13/bitcoin-etfs-herald-less-febrile-token-longer-term-traders-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 13 Jul 2024 15:53:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
